      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a professional double-VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and silent. The suspension geometry is dialed to factory specifications, utilizing fresh bushings to maintain the chassis' legendary feedback. With all VIN tags intact and a pristine undercarriage, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking a linear power band and 8,000 RPM capability.",
